'''Valentin Zlatev''' ({{lang-bg|Валентин Златев}}) (born 8 December 1965) is a [[Bulgaria]]n businessman who is the Bulgarian representative of the Russian oil giant [[LUKoil]] and the president of basketball club [[Lukoil Akademik]].<ref name="livemedia66.bg">{{cite news|url=http://pdf.cloud.livemedia.bg/2011/04/30/livesport_article_16889.pdf|title=Валентин Златев отложи срещата с баскетбола, дългоочакваната среща между членовете на УС на Федерацията и Валентин Златев отново бе отложена|publisher=livemedia.bg|date=2011-04-30|language=Bulgarian|accessdate=2014-12-13}}</ref>
He is married to Lyuba Stefanova, who won the Miss Plovdiv competition in 2001, and they have three children - a two sons named Vasil and Anton and a daughter called Kristina.<ref name="slava66.bg">{{cite news|url=http://www.slava.bg/profiles/592.html|title=Профил на Валентин Златев|publisher=slava.bg|date= |language=Bulgarian|accessdate=2014-12-13}}</ref>
